1) because some paths get displayed in their absolute form
   extract (cvs-update) package to

   /root/src/ucon64/src/...

   or the checksums of some outputs will be false calculated
2) uncomment 

   #define TEST

   in ucon64.c
3) run "./configure --without-zlib && make && make install"
4) copy test/ to /tmp
5) copy test/test.dat to ~/.ucon64/dat/
6) run "./ucon64"
